= Weekly meal plan

- Courses : Every saturday
    You can buy fresh fish





Monday : Fish
    200-300g maquereau (surgelé) 
    + fried cheese
    + whatever you like.. : cuisse poulet braisée, fruits de mer, etc..

Thuesday : 400g entrecote + 200-300g lamb liver (Go to boucher here)
wednsday : 400g entrecote
thursday : 400g entrecote 
friday : 400g entrecote(Go to boucher here) + 200g poumons/testicules/coeur d'agneau/rognons/tete agneau(debut de chaque mois)
saturday : 400g entrecote
Sunday : 400g entrecote + 2 cotes agneau(YOU HAVE in CONGELATEUR)

9 eggs/day
    soft boiled
    medium boiled
    fried whole
    scrambled
        + butter
        + cheese
        + some meat : merguez, crevette, jambon, steak, liver...

Steak haché + some cheese (fake cheddar, tomme savoie, etc)
    Fill in the blanks


200g cheese/day
    AOP/IGP lait cru : to eat raw
    AOP/IGP pasteurisé : steaks, eggs, fried
    other cheeses : fried, steaks


- Cost : Less than 450e/month
- Nutrition :
    Omega 3 : 500g mackerel
        Worst case : 55(makerel) + 15 (lamb) = 70g/week (1.54:1)
        Best case : 55(makerel) + 15 (lamb) +  7(cheese) = 77 (1.69:1)
    Omega 6 :
         5/2(chicken) + 5(beef) + 6(steak haché) + 25(eggs) + 7(cheese) = 45.5


Around 450e/month

